name: FLY
description:
“When night falls, a miracle happens on this sea: at the very horizon it breaks off, giving access to open space. It will be enough just to take one step and you will be able to take off, and you will be able to take off on your feet will no longer be. Only infinite height. This will be your last flight of unlimited freedom, before yours turns into a burning club of gas, giving others the light of hope. I sit on this shore for hours and watch the stars await the birth of a new star. - 
Marina Matisse 1991 year
